Notes: Pointers lead 29-10, but Pioneers cut lead to 33-28 by half ...
Pioneers come within 33-31, but UWSP answers with 13-2 run ... UWP comes
within 4 at 68-64 with 17.7 seconds left, but Heuer makes 1-2 FT and
Schultz makes 2-2 to seal win for defending NCAA III national champions.
Game.Officials: Blaine Hilgendorf,  Brian Kenney,  Dennis Inderdahl
